snippet.textDisplay:
Sukhwinder is great singer but i think Divya Kumar was more suitable for this song. Divya Kumar has that smoothness and versatility in his voice which easily matches with corresponding singer's voice. whereas Sukhwinder more suitable for solo ventures with his sharp and soothing voice. 
But here Jasmine Sandlas took the song to a completely new level. Wud love to see her in more and more collaborations up ahead. perfect voice for Sufi attire.
